folder: Fresh Pond Road & Catalpa Avenue, Queens, NY
original_title: Queens: Fresh Pond Road - Catalpa Avenue
text:
Fresh Pond Road (tracks thereon), at the S.W. corner of Catalpa Ave., showing the John C. De Bevoise house from 1852 to 1873.  This house which has been added to is now occupied by the Ridgewood Court (K. of C.) and the Fifth District City Magistrates Court, which opened here on March 15, 1922.  In View No. 1, Public School No. 88 is partially seen at the extreme right.

1922.
Views 1 and 3.
View 2: March 1923.

Eugene L, Armbruster Collection.
